__MAKE__and__MAKEFILE__

PAHANJ@__make utilitayi mijocov kazmakerpel .cpp ev .hpp fileri build proces@:

Arajadranq@ katarvac e tarber astichani bardutyunnerov.

1: unecac src/.cpp ev header/.hpp ev makefile@ gtnvum en nujn katalogum, makefi|
le@ chi parunakum popoxakanner.
2: nuyn@ miajn en tarberutyamb vor makefile@ grvac e popoxakannerov.
3: ajstex arden make hramani ardyunqum arajacox .o ev exe fileer@ texadrvum en |
naxoroq stexcvac /obj ev /bin katalognerum.
4: nujn@ miajn en tarberutyamb vor /obj ev /bin katalogner@ stexcvum en avtomat|
ev nranc mej texadrum@ nujnpes katarvum e avtomat.
4_dep: nujn@ miajn en tarberubyamb vor kaxvacutyunner@ include en arvum .dep fi|
lic.
5: ajs tarberakum 4: tarberaki himan vra lucvac e mek ajl xndir.Goyutyun unecox|
.cpp file@ build e arvum ajpes vor .cpp um grvac "kuku" bari poxaren tpvi mek u|
rish artahajtutyun ev .cpp um trvac 10 angami poxaren, mek ajl qanakov.

